{"tid":2414531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財長耶倫：美國多方面需與中國合作","createTime":"2021-02-19T12:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T09:03:17.000Z","uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"301e3c27b1dc297f9d7464b88cc128c3e1b4fe79","tid":2414531,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"蘋果全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210219/IXFR5PJHKBF7RN6KJAD6WVTQPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2FIXFR5PJHKBF7RN6KJAD6WVTQPY%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=bc58ee89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2FIXFR5PJHKBF7RN6KJAD6WVTQPY%2F&h=cb069b8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210219/IXFR5PJHKBF7RN6KJAD6WVTQPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國財長耶倫表示，美國目前會保留特朗普政府對中國貨品徵收的關稅，但會進行全面檢討，此後再決定未來路向。耶倫稱美國希望確保中國在貿易、技術轉移等問題上恪守國際規範，但也指中美需要在氣候變化、抗疫等多方面合作。<br />\n<br />\n耶倫周四接受財經頻道CNBC訪問時強調，美國期望北京遵守貿易承諾，華府正審視對華政策，又稱在研究不公平貿易行為時有「一系列問題」，美方亦關注中國有關強制技術轉移及補貼高科技企業的行為，期望可促使中國遵守國際規範。被問到此前的關稅是否有效時，耶倫稍為遲疑後回答說：「我們將看看。」"},{"pid":"82f2ede9a8e0d7c1c58b859bc3bfa8c9b247f17c","tid":2414531,"uid":258903,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"舖路奶共"},{"pid":"68b79db5fa821adbb8866ec87c678598fcc76932","tid":2414531,"uid":99962,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e8eaeacd70da570b831abb5695a696b6ebfd02","tid":2414531,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:17:25.000Z","msg":"有冇收支那錢去演講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee367cab5eb531651b5a728